# Flutter App — English UI Only

All user-facing strings in the Flutter app must be **English only**. No Myanmar/Burmese text in UI labels, buttons, messages, or dialogs.

Chat with the user may be in Myanmar; the app UI is English.

## Product reference

Match **Lotaya Dinga** style and feature set over time:
- Points balance, tiers, daily check-in
- Quizzes / games to earn points
- Classroom / education content (future)
- Reward ads (AdMob, future)
- Public ID for external redemption
- No in-app cash withdraw UI (Play Store policy) — exchange website only

## API config

Production URLs via dart-define only:
- `API_URL`
- `EXCHANGE_URL`
